snippet.title: Sonic Red Ridge - SAGE 2021 Release
snippet.description:
[Sonic Inifinty Plus] Sonic Red Ridge [Development video 5]

SFGHQ DOWNLOAD: https://sonicfangameshq.com/forums/showcase/sonic-red-ridge.1005/
GAMEJOLT DOWNLOAD: https://gamejolt.com/games/sonicreforge/454452

Credits
Tigersonalex: Game Design, Level Design...
Philemon Holmes (Lemonhead VGM): Level Background Song, Main Menu Song

Infinity Plus: Unreal 3D Sonic Framework (Game programming, animation assembling, objects interactions...)
